sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User<br/>(nvsnap thaw / API)
    participant Srv as nvsnap-server
    participant K8s as K8s API
    participant Pod as restore Pod<br/>(scheduled on N2)
    participant Init as init containers
    participant Agent as nvsnap-agent<br/>(node N2)
    participant PeerN1 as nvsnap-agent<br/>(node N1, source)
    participant Blob as nvsnap-blobstore
    participant Entry as restore-entrypoint
    participant CRIU as CRIU
    participant CC as cuda-checkpoint

    User->>Srv: POST /restore/pod {ckptID, target}
    Srv->>K8s: apply restore Pod manifest<br/>(nodeName: N2)
    K8s->>Pod: schedule
    Pod->>Init: get-uvloop, get-libuv, get-libzmq, get-criu run
    Init->>Init: populate /nvsnap-lib emptyDir<br/>(wheels, libs, sitecustomize)

    Pod->>Agent: restore container starts<br/>(LD_PRELOAD on, PYTHONPATH set)
    Agent->>Agent: cascade fetch checkpoint
    Agent->>Agent: tier-1: local hostPath check
    alt local hit
        Agent-->>Pod: ready
    else miss
        Agent->>PeerN1: HTTP GET /peer/<ckptID>
        alt peer hit
            PeerN1-->>Agent: stream chunks
        else peer miss
            Agent->>Blob: GET <ckptID>
            Blob-->>Agent: stream chunks
        end
        Agent->>Agent: write to hostPath
    end

    Pod->>Entry: exec /nvsnap/restore-entrypoint
    Entry->>CC: prep GPU state restore<br/>(from nvidia-files.img)
    Entry->>CRIU: restore --tree=<pid> --external=dev[195/0]:nvidia0 ...
    CRIU->>CRIU: rebuild fd table, vmas, memory
    CRIU->>CC: CUDA plugin: replay RM ioctls, H2D copy
    CC-->>CRIU: GPU state restored
    CRIU->>Pod: resume process tree

    Pod->>Pod: process resumes inside restored memory image
    Pod->>Pod: patched uvloop's uv_loop_fork() reinits libuv state
    Pod-->>User: inference resumes (/v1/completions OK)

    Note over Pod,Entry: NIM 8B restore: ~1 min from pod ready to inference
